  "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-main relative\"\u003e\n \u003ch1 class\u003d\"block text-[4rem] text-[var(--dark)] leading-[4.4rem] font-semibold mb-[5px]\"\u003e\u0026Ocirc;ng Rubio: Mỹ kh\u0026ocirc;ng đổi ch\u0026iacute;nh s\u0026aacute;ch về Đ\u0026agrave;i Loan để đạt thỏa thuận thương mại với Trung Quốc\u003c/h1\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-meta flex items-center flex-wrap flex-row text-[1.3rem] leading-[2rem] font-normal text-[#999] truncate h-[30px] mb-[10px] [\u0026amp;\u0026gt;:not(:first-child)]:ml-[25px]\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"flex items-center\"\u003e\n   \u003ca href\u003d\"/bao-phap-luat-tp-hcm-plo-p114.epi\" class\u003d\"bm-card-source flex items-center shrink-0\" title\u003d\"B\u0026aacute;o Ph\u0026aacute;p Luật TP.HCM\"\u003e\n    \u003cfigure class\u003d\"image opacity-80 w-auto h-[16px]\" style\u003d\"width:55px;height:20px\" aria-label\u003d\"Logo nh\u0026agrave; xuất bản\"\u003e\n     \u003cpicture\u003e\n      \u003csource srcset\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/f12dd0420d01e45fbd10.png\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n      \u003csource srcset\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/f12dd0420d01e45fbd10.png\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n      \u003cimg src\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/f12dd0420d01e45fbd10.png\" alt\u003d\"B\u0026aacute;o Ph\u0026aacute;p Luật TP.HCM\" width\u003d\"176\" height\u003d\"64\" /\u003e\n     \u003c/picture\u003e\n    \u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n   \u003cspan\u003e\u003cbutton class\u003d\"relative text-[14px] leading-[normal] font-normal text-center cursor-pointer normal-case border-0 transition-button disabled:shadow-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed follow-button flex items-center item-star ml-[10px]\" tabindex\u003d\"0\" type\u003d\"button\" title\u003d\"Theo d\u0026otilde;i \u0026quot;PLO\u0026quot;\" aria-label\u003d\"Button\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"icon inline-block font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-star text-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003ctime datetime\u003d\"2025-10-26T01:05:44.000Z\"\u003e13 giờ trước\u003c/time\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d\"/marco-rubio-t38990132.epi\" class\u003d\"related inline !text-[#adb5bd] hover:!text-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e344\n   \u003c!-- --\u003e li\u0026ecirc;n quan\u003c/a\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d\"/ong-rubio-my-khong-doi-chinh-sach-ve-dai-loan-de-dat-thoa-thuan-thuong-mai-voi-trung-quoc-r53586608.epi\" class\u003d\"origin item-origin\" target\u003d\"_blank\" rel\u003d\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"icon inline-block font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-copy text-[13px] mr-[5px]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGốc\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003ch3 class\u003d\"sapo block text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] font-semibold text-[var(--dark)] p-[10px] bg-[#f2f4f5]\"\u003eNgoại trưởng Mỹ Marco Rubio n\u0026oacute;i rằng Washington kh\u0026ocirc;ng nghĩ tới chuyện thay đổi ch\u0026iacute;nh s\u0026aacute;ch về Đ\u0026agrave;i Loan để đạt được thỏa thuận thương mại với Trung Quốc.\u003c/h3\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-body text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] text-black mt-[15px] break-words overflow-hidden [\u0026amp;_h1]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h2]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h3]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h4]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h5]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_p]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;\u0026gt;div]:mb-[15px]\"\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eNg\u0026agrave;y 25-10, Ngoại trưởng Mỹ \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/marco-rubio-tag14811.epi\"\u003eMarco Rubio\u003c/a\u003e n\u0026oacute;i rằng ch\u0026iacute;nh quyền Tổng thống Mỹ Donald Trump sẽ kh\u0026ocirc;ng từ bỏ ch\u0026iacute;nh s\u0026aacute;ch l\u0026acirc;u nay về Đ\u0026agrave;i Loan để đạt được một thỏa thuận thương mại khi đ\u0026agrave;m ph\u0026aacute;n với Trung Quốc, theo h\u0026atilde;ng tin \u003cem\u003eBloomberg\u003c/em\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003e“Nếu ai đ\u0026oacute; lo ngại rằng ch\u0026uacute;ng ta sẽ đạt được một thỏa thuận thương mại c\u0026oacute; lợi để đổi lấy việc quay lưng với \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/dai-loan-tag91.epi\"\u003eĐ\u0026agrave;i Loan\u003c/a\u003e, th\u0026igrave; xin n\u0026oacute;i r\u0026otilde;, kh\u0026ocirc;ng ai trong ch\u0026iacute;nh quyền nghĩ đến điều đ\u0026oacute;” - \u0026ocirc;ng Rubio n\u0026oacute;i với c\u0026aacute;c ph\u0026oacute;ng vi\u0026ecirc;n tr\u0026ecirc;n chuyến bay từ Israel đến Qatar h\u0026ocirc;m 25-10.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url(\u0027https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png\u0027)] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\"\u003e\n   \u003ci class\u003d\"icon font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\n   \u003cbutton class\u003d\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style\u003d\"width:625px;height:416px\"\u003e\n    \u003cpicture\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\" Ngoại trưởng Mỹ Marco Rubio. Ảnh: Aaron Schwartz/CNP/Bloomberg \" width\u003d\"625\" height\u003d\"416\" /\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"\u003e\u003cem\u003e Ngoại trưởng Mỹ Marco Rubio. Ảnh: Aaron Schwartz/CNP/Bloomberg \u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTrước đ\u0026oacute;, khi được hỏi về ch\u0026iacute;nh s\u0026aacute;ch của Mỹ đối với Đ\u0026agrave;i Loan tr\u0026ecirc;n chuy\u0026ecirc;n cơ Air Force One, \u0026ocirc;ng \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/donald-trump-tag673.epi\"\u003eTrump\u003c/a\u003e tỏ ra thận trọng: “T\u0026ocirc;i kh\u0026ocirc;ng muốn b\u0026agrave;n về vấn đề đ\u0026oacute; l\u0026uacute;c n\u0026agrave;y. T\u0026ocirc;i kh\u0026ocirc;ng muốn l\u0026agrave;m mọi thứ trở n\u0026ecirc;n phức tạp hơn”.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003ePh\u0026iacute;a \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/trung-quoc-tag101.epi\"\u003eTrung Quốc\u003c/a\u003e chưa l\u0026ecirc;n tiếng về th\u0026ocirc;ng tin tr\u0026ecirc;n.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003ePh\u0026aacute;t biểu của \u0026ocirc;ng Rubio được đưa ra trong bối cảnh Chủ tịch Trung Quốc Tập Cận B\u0026igrave;nh đang th\u0026uacute;c giục Mỹ điều chỉnh ch\u0026iacute;nh s\u0026aacute;ch “một Trung Quốc”, y\u0026ecirc;u cầu Washington tuy\u0026ecirc;n bố c\u0026ocirc;ng khai rằng họ “phản đối độc lập Đ\u0026agrave;i Loan”.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u0026Ocirc;ng Trump dự kiến gặp \u0026ocirc;ng Tập tại H\u0026agrave;n Quốc v\u0026agrave;o ng\u0026agrave;y 30-10, b\u0026ecirc;n lề khổ Hội nghị Cấp cao Hợp t\u0026aacute;c Kinh tế ch\u0026acirc;u \u0026Aacute; - Th\u0026aacute;i B\u0026igrave;nh Dương (APEC). Đ\u0026acirc;y sẽ l\u0026agrave; cuộc gặp trực tiếp đầu ti\u0026ecirc;n giữa hai nh\u0026agrave; l\u0026atilde;nh đạo kể từ khi \u0026ocirc;ng Trump trở lại Nh\u0026agrave; Trắng hồi th\u0026aacute;ng 1.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eĐ\u0026agrave;i Loan từ l\u0026acirc;u l\u0026agrave; điểm n\u0026oacute;ng nhạy cảm trong quan hệ Mỹ-Trung, vốn đ\u0026atilde; căng thẳng v\u0026igrave; c\u0026aacute;c vấn đề thương mại v\u0026agrave; c\u0026ocirc;ng nghệ.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eBắc Kinh coi Đ\u0026agrave;i Loan l\u0026agrave; một phần l\u0026atilde;nh thổ kh\u0026ocirc;ng thể t\u0026aacute;ch rời với đại lục v\u0026agrave; tuy\u0026ecirc;n bố c\u0026oacute; thể thống nhất bằng vũ lực nếu cần thiết.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eMỹ hiện l\u0026agrave; đối t\u0026aacute;c quốc ph\u0026ograve;ng lớn nhất của Đ\u0026agrave;i Bắc, d\u0026ugrave; \u0026ocirc;ng Trump từng gợi \u0026yacute; rằng h\u0026ograve;n đảo “n\u0026ecirc;n trả ph\u0026iacute; bảo vệ” cho Washington.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text body-author text-right\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDƯƠNG KHANG\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp\" tabindex\u003d\"-1\" role\u003d\"dialog\" aria-hidden\u003d\"true\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__bg\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__scroll-wrap\"\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__container\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__ui pswp__ui--hidden\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__top-bar\"\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__counter\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--close\" title\u003d\"Close 